<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Munka után, az esti órákban végezhető:</span><a href="https://www.becube.hu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener external" data-wpel-link="external"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">BeCube</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">,</span><a href="https://www.prooktatas.hu/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener external" data-wpel-link="external"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Pro Oktatás</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">,</span><a href="https://www.greenfoxacademy.com/junior-programozo-kepzeseink/reszidos-kepzes" target="_blank" rel="noopener external" data-wpel-link="external"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Green Fox Academy</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">,</span><a href="https://www.flowacademy.hu/flow-work" target="_blank" rel="noopener external" data-wpel-link="external"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">Flow Academy</span></a></li>
